Class NoOpMetadataManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.physical.impl.scan.project.NoOpMetadataManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetadataManager

    public class NoOpMetadataManager
extends Object
implements MetadataManager
    Do-nothing implementation of the metadata manager. Allows the metadata manager to be optional without needing an if-statement on every access.
